  //- Discography Section
  #discography.text-center
    .container
      .section-title.center
        h2 Music
        hr
        p
          |Also check #[a(href='http://soundcloud.com/6ow3idgirl') SoundCloud] and #[a(href='https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_vCY6ONyh2STh02OFTdSTA?view_as=subscriber') Official YouTube Channel] !! 
