          img(src='/images/portfolio/01-jacket.jpg', class='img-responsive', alt='project title')
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6.skill
          h4 peko-niko-boo!
          img(src='/images/portfolio/02-jacket.jpg', class='img-responsive', alt='project title')
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6.skill
          h4 Third Release coming soon ... !!
          img(src='/images/coming-soon-lg-rotate.png', class='img-responsive', alt='project title')

  //- Photo section
  #portfolio
    .container
      .section-title.text-center.center
        h2 YouTube
        hr
        p
          |Full YouTube official channel is available #[a(href='https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_vCY6ONyh2STh02OFTdSTA/featured') Here] !!
      .categories
        ul.cat
          li
            ol.type
              li
                a(href='#' data-filter='*', class='active') All
              li
                a(href='#' data-filter='.web') MVs
              li
                a(href='#' data-filter='.app') Others
        .clearfix
      .row
        .portfolio-items
          //- Replace thumbnails for each movie
          .col-sm-6.col-md-3.col-lg-3.web
            .portfolio-item
              .hover-bg
                a(href='https://youtu.be/8mE0SY7WW74', title='Released on 2020/04/25', rel='prettyPhoto')
                  .hover-text
                    h4 Whack a mole
                  img(src='/images/portfolio/01-thumb.jpg', class='img-responsive', alt='Whack a mole')
          .col-sm-6.col-md-3.col-lg-3.web
            .portfolio-item
              .hover-bg
                a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g1EETsO1Xx8', title='Released on 2020/05/13', rel='prettyPhoto')
                  .hover-text
                    h4 peko-niko-boo!
                  img(src='/images/portfolio/02-thumb.jpg', class='img-responsive', alt='peko-niko-boo!')
          .col-sm-6.col-md-3.col-lg-3.web
            .portfolio-item
              .hover-bg
                a(href='/images/comming-soon-lg-rotate.png', title='Comming-Soon', rel='prettyPhoto')
                  .hover-text
                    h4 Comming Soon ...!!
                  img(src='/images/coming-soon-lg-rotate.png', class='img-responsive', alt='tbd-next-single-name')

  //- Biography Section
  #biography.text-center
    .container
      .section-titile.center
        h2 Biography
        hr
      .row
        .col-md-12.text-center
          h3 6ow 3id girl (ローミッドガール)
          img(class='img-responsive', src='/images/about.jpg')
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          .about-text
            p.text-center
              |2020年始動。女性ベースシンガーソングライター。
              br
              |ベーシストであり、シンガーソングライター。
              br
              |アレンジ、ミックス、マスタリング、映像編集等を通じて
              br
              |総合的に世界観を表現する。
              br
              |まだ誰も見たことのない世界へ。
            p.text-center
              |since 2020. Female bass singer-songwriter.
              br
              |She is a bassist and singer-songwriter,
              br
              |and she comprehensively expresses the worldview
              br
              |through arrangement, mixing, mastering, and video editing etc...
              br
              |A new world that you never seen.

